{"tid":1503774,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"我朋友做m記會整 口水可樂、痰汁比藍絲／差佬食","createTime":"2019-08-25T05:36:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T13:44:58.000Z","uid":128705,"like":141,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"8552500daf6ea3fa6f09e617a0a2b3067e070897","tid":1503774,"uid":128705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:36:49.000Z","msg":"琴晚落吧飲酒我朋友飲大左話佢係m記，表面六折優惠撐警，對差佬好支持。<br />\n<br />\n但係每次有差佬嚟點餐落單，櫃檯都會標明顯示係police，然後入面廚房砌包果時就會加料<br />\n<br />\n有汁既包就會吐痰、HI一HI屎忽窿，插隻手指落啲汁到，撈勻再上<br />\n汽水咖啡就會吐口水<br />\n薯條就加頭皮落去當鹽<br />\n<br />\n最正係魚柳bell<br />\n如果個差佬叫魚柳Bell，加口水呢啲小不免，最癲係即場打飛機射落包入面同大雞醬撈埋先比差佬食。<br />\n有次個廚房癲癲地，專登大聲同櫃檯講：「魚撚包呀～」全餐廳啲員工都係度忍笑，經理頂唔順大大聲笑出嚟，個差佬仲要懞盛盛坐低食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：我朋友醉醉地果陣講，事後有講話係發夢見到"},{"pid":"b9aa4581187291b55608056d8ea801f04b73083f","tid":1503774,"uid":110509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:37:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月1 (日) 一定係機場</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">9月14中秋,未必CALL 到人, 所以</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月7 (六), 9 月8(日) 連續2日一定係機場</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">全部1點，唯一底線，唔衝禁區(會變恐襲)</span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">之後既每個星期六/日 要起碼有一日一定係機場，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乜撚都要讓路!!</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n聽日826 仲有國泰城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f681350eb40ea0a3ecf550c883b5acfcb121886b","tid":1503774,"uid":178791,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:38:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小事啦<br />\n黑警出街都食慣"},{"pid":"fb11196a202a3c20c9eace56bf8324b3c844a78f","tid":1503774,"uid":129016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:39:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b727d8fcbcf8f4ad51636b53f29b884b9d91fe","tid":1503774,"uid":248588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:40:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ce44cb3262ff2b96c83f28573aa6aa4f6c8b7d","tid":1503774,"uid":181474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:42:10.000Z","msg":"已經變潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bbd3512084c4512249efd9a87411bce59e0cfff","tid":1503774,"uid":65210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:42:38.000Z","msg":"［開飯/住宿/義診/搵工］你班前線死廢青 未成年中學雞同我入黎！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1503091\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1503091</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ecc3e31d51b50ba52a1e02395918c60952fed00f","tid":1503774,"uid":152262,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:43:11.000Z","msg":"傷心浩園餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99e139664a168728b843db7bbb1d7ba08ab9b6c","tid":1503774,"uid":206357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:43:54.000Z","msg":"高汁"},{"pid":"3931b34beea411ed4ceca447d8499d69079dbd59","tid":1503774,"uid":49128,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:49:13.000Z","msg":"屌，唔好朋友啦<br />\n<br />\n自己入去做啦<br />\n<br />\n大家學生哥宜排遊行冇咩錢<br />\n<br />\n當搵d錢食飯啦<br />\n<br />\n再加料比藍絲廢老警察<br />\n<br />\nPt比人發現咪走<br />\n<br />\n驚閪咩"},{"pid":"32008db563343d16f7a6e6bc1796d364d5628420","tid":1503774,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:57:25.000Z","msg":"鳩汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e8bde0ea105035b4801ea2e9e0aede362c5440","tid":1503774,"uid":61084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:02:21.000Z","msg":"魚撚包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"632104f7165433b1ce23bb8323662db81d0ce4e1","tid":1503774,"uid":53361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:29:41.000Z","msg":"中港M記係有經營權<br />\n但個品牌一樣係M記<br />\n而M記個招牌同形象係咪真係支持human rights架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麥當勞作為國際大公司<br />\n又係美國股市上市<br />\n仲要係自己web page Missions &amp; Values 到寫 Respect Human Rights<br />\n<a href=\"https://corporate.mcdonalds.com/corpmcd/scale-for-good/our-people-and-communities/respecting-human-rights.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.mcdonalds.com%2Fcorpmcd%2Fscale-for-good%2Four-people-and-communities%2Frespecting-human-rights.html&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUKDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=ee436d19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://corporate.mcdonalds.com/corpmcd/scale-for-good/our-people-and-communities/respecting-human-rights.html</a><br />\n但係又比六折犯人道罪既香港警察<br />\n行為同說話都唔同既<br />\n咁係咪應該問下總公司佢地個立埸係咩呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nsend email去呢到<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mcdonalds.com/press/press-contacts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mcdonalds.com%2Fpress%2Fpress-contacts&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUKDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=a011a4dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mcdonalds.com/press/press-contacts</a><br />\n美國巴絲可以直接打電話去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c32a